{"tid":1477381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"818如果 維園滿左 去邊","createTime":"2019-08-16T06:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T07:21:42.000Z","uid":227788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"04897af06d669c414ab85531f85bf99948b5bf68","tid":1477381,"uid":227788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:04:59.000Z","msg":"接機 ?"},{"pid":"dcbc62aa6c82bba1dccf553a11cde70dcb242ec5","tid":1477381,"uid":269681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:07:43.000Z","msg":"滿左照行？ 無啦啦港島咁多人轉去機場 中間個流失會好高"},{"pid":"1fba1169271481832105985382b698b84b194606","tid":1477381,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:13:44.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0836f6345f2efbeb895f13991d6091e62f27fd1c","tid":1477381,"uid":258770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:14:54.000Z","msg":"無辦法 唯有排隊入去<br />\n唔知隊尾去唔去到中聯辦呢"},{"pid":"0c78912c045641f3ef60cfebd739bbe0cf61ecc8","tid":1477381,"uid":232817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:15:46.000Z","msg":"滿先算啦，依家乜宣傳都冇！"},{"pid":"278ada314415b5c6621afb3c654cf8ba20821509","tid":1477381,"uid":277702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:16:49.000Z","msg":"民陣都未諗拈點搞..."},{"pid":"322d0a62dee30ba3a98ee0455f287feaa9023080","tid":1477381,"uid":279616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:18:59.000Z","msg":"相信民間智慧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推到漫山遍野連儂牆818五大訴求文宣（追究721 85 811），重申七一宣言，定立死線<br />\n<br />\n唔係仇警，大家一定要清楚知道點解要清算警隊。警暴（濫捕、濫告、不依法規）係暴政一部分，唔全面改革警隊、監警制度，只會令目前同將來爭取雙普選更加舉步維艱<br />\n<br />\n所以，絕對唔需要否認自己係針對警隊，針對警隊就係對準政權。唔通你淨係針對林鄭、唔針對政制，就會有雙普選？<br />\n<br />\n#唔撤就罷<br />\n#罷工罷巿罷買罷課<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與全港三罷<br />\n#各區集會<br />\n#出核彈麻包袋都唔割蓆<br />\n#直至政府跪低<br />\n#解散警隊<br />\n#永遠抵制元朗荃灣北角所有商戶<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動"},{"pid":"c520138395a9e1c24df46aa9d4a2a716a14bc51d","tid":1477381,"uid":227788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"278ada314415b5c6621afb3c654cf8ba20821509","tid":1477381,"uid":277702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:16:49.000Z","msg":"民陣都未諗拈點搞..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:22:27.000Z","msg":"冇乜時間。<br />\n佢唔可以公開叫人做D乜。"},{"pid":"a53fd58e240a1436bb99b351f1509f9184773d10","tid":1477381,"uid":279167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:46:55.000Z","msg":"我好守法的，會由北角開始排隊入維園"},{"pid":"794d85c502e4b4af1df55c61f2ae891afcbe7fc5","tid":1477381,"uid":277702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:21:42.000Z","msg":"最好統一時間，大家用自己方法去維園"}]}